com.inrix.sdk.model

Class TravelTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.model.TravelTime

  • public class TravelTime
extends Object
    Represents a prediction of a travel time in a particular route starting at a particular departure time or ending at a particular arrival time. This class contains the travel time for that departure time or arrival time and it also contains additional information such as road closures, restrictions, average speed and any abnormality travel time in minutes.
